    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>``` coffeescript
jQuery ->
  $('#input_field').autocomplete</p>

<pre><code>source: $('#input_field').data('autocomplete-source')
select: (event, ui) -&gt;
  $("#input_field").val(ui.item.value)
  $('#form').submit()
</code></pre>

